.TH ePing 8 "2013" Linux Ericsson
.SH NAME
ePing \- A cross-platform flexible ping utility for the 21st century.
.SH SYNOPSYS
.B ./ePing.out ADDRESS [OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B ePing
is an implementation of the class ping utility with added functionality. It uses the ICMP's ECHO_REQUEST to elicit an ECHO_REPLY from a host. Uses OpenMP for multithreading.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-q ", " \-\-request\-time \fItimeBetweenPings\fR
Set the length of time in milliseconds between pings. Default is 1000 ms.
